{"tid":2029463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【贈慶】新任財庫局局長許正宇到訪破產管理署了解電子提交文件系統","createTime":"2020-05-22T08:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T16:49:26.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec4e5f71c8c2ef146249172b5d39893fea320b1","tid":2029463,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202005/22/P2020052200524_photo_1175970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F22%2FP2020052200524_photo_1175970.jpg&h=c5cfe590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/22/P2020052200524.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F22%2FP2020052200524.htm&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=15c6cf88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/22/P2020052200524.htm</a><br />\n<blockquote>財經事務及庫務局局長到訪破產管理署<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇今日（五月二十二日）到訪破產管理署，<span style=\"color: red;\">了解該署提供的破產和清盤服務。</span><br />\n  許正宇在破產管理署署長麥錦羅陪同下，到訪個案處理部轄下的快速處理個案組，聽取同事簡介債務人呈請破產個案的處理程序，<span style=\"color: red;\">以及破產管理署打算推行的電子提交文件系統。</span><br />\n  他指出，隨着經濟環境變差及失業率上升，破產和清盤個案的數字會傾向增加，<span style=\"color: red;\">破產管理署會密切留意新收個案數目，並會考慮合適可行措施，簡化各項工作程序，以及使用資訊科技提升效率，以應付更多個案數目。</span><br />\n  電子提交文件系統是一站式平台，接收不同持份者以電子方式提交的文件及表格，並為文件及表格加上時間戳記，可提升處理破產和清盤個案的效率。許正宇表示，政府稍後會向立法會財務委員會提交撥款申請。<br />\n <br />\n  許正宇隨後巡視了公眾查詢櫃台，了解破產管理署提供的破產和強制清盤呈請服務，以及破產案、個人自願安排個案及強制清盤案的查冊服務。<br />\n <br />\n  行程結束前，許正宇與部門同事會面，聽取他們講解工作情況，並感謝他們在疫情下努力不懈地為市民提供公共服務。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年5月22日（星期五）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/about/govdirectory/po/sfst.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fgovdirectory%2Fpo%2Fsfst.htm&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=d6795241\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/about/govdirectory/po/sfst.htm</a><br />\n許正宇於1999年至2003年期間出任特區政府政務主任，曾被調派到經濟發展科、香港特區政府駐北京辦事處和民政事務總署服務。他在2003年離開政府後曾任職銀行界，<span style=\"color: red;\">其後在香港交易所工作長達十多年</span>，並自2019年起出任香港金融發展局行政總監。"},{"pid":"0d2f0269445723cbb8f5d79759490ad52ec9e092","tid":2029463,"uid":125502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"d29e39c8f4c242bf84d006eab0097c145eda4be4","tid":2029463,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:49:36.000Z","msg":"破產管理署署長麥錦羅（右三）<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202005/22/P2020052200524_photo_1175972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F22%2FP2020052200524_photo_1175972.jpg&h=87eae2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201701/24/P2017012400290_photo_1112389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201701%2F24%2FP2017012400290_photo_1112389.jpg&h=b95ed628&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e3c889e330d42349e434e791cead96451351027","tid":2029463,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d2f0269445723cbb8f5d79759490ad52ec9e092","tid":2029463,"uid":125502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"bot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16904b3c65f9fb243fec4f425e54f010b4813d7","tid":2029463,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"叫埋林鄭去啦 佢民望都破產"},{"pid":"2431dd7dcca1ec321a43e07f9046ff482445dc59","tid":2029463,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"琴日去咁多到，今日剩係去破產管理署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/21/P2020052100717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F21%2FP2020052100717.htm&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=a0493b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/21/P2020052100717.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202005/21/P2020052100717_photo_1175962.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F21%2FP2020052100717_photo_1175962.jpg&h=efc2bc7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n稅務局<br />\n察看員工處理報稅表及僱主電子報税服務的流程。該局自去年底開始接受「轉數快」繳付稅款，為市民提供多一個便利的繳税方法。許正宇指政府正安排逐步將服務擴展至其他部門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202005/21/P2020052100717_photo_1175960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F21%2FP2020052100717_photo_1175960.jpg&h=ade7bb02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商業登記署<br />\n了解因應2019冠狀病毒病疫情而實施的商業登記櫃位服務安排。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202005/21/P2020052100717_photo_1175967.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F21%2FP2020052100717_photo_1175967.jpg&h=a722b21b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n庫務署<br />\n了解$10,000現金發放計劃相關的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">籌備</span></span>工作進度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202005/21/P2020052100717_photo_1175969.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F21%2FP2020052100717_photo_1175969.jpg&h=b2a8a029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府統計處<br />\n聽取2021年人口普查的籌備情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202005/21/P2020052100717_photo_1175964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F21%2FP2020052100717_photo_1175964.jpg&h=29adb5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貿易統計數據服務中心和電腦輔助電話訪問中心<br />\n了解他們的日常工作。"},{"pid":"7c392d0fe18543ca1c536a74d248c1181bc00af7","tid":2029463,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d16904b3c65f9fb243fec4f425e54f010b4813d7","tid":2029463,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"叫埋林鄭去啦 佢民望都破產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"負家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598310c2a52a79f8a40dbbe16e9b8c684445a7fb","tid":2029463,"uid":247298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"第一張右邊more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6c216a981a7d13edd20db84438f99c1c8870d1","tid":2029463,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"51歲（電子交表）"},{"pid":"8a4a6d60edcbace32c04d0d67f89abb2e859fbca","tid":2029463,